# 🌸 My Magical Day ✨

> A kawaii pixel-art daily planner web app — a cuter, more magical upgrade of the original "Digital Typewriter" receipt printer concept.

***

## 📸 Preview

A pastel pixel-art themed daily planner that lets you add events and to-dos, pick your mood, and "print" a beautiful kawaii receipt for your day — complete with confetti hearts, sparkle effects, and animated backgrounds.

***

## ✨ Features

- 🖨️ **Animated Pixel Printer** — A bouncy pixel printer that dramatically prints your daily receipt with heart confetti flying out
- 📝 **Editable Events & To-Dos** — Add, manage, and delete your own events (with time + category) and to-do items (with priority stars)
- 😊 **Mood Picker** — Choose your daily mood from 6 pixel emoji options before printing
- 🌟 **Live Progress Bar** — A pixel health-bar style progress tracker that updates as you check off tasks
- 💬 **Daily Affirmations** — A rotating kawaii quote appears at the bottom of every receipt
- 🌸 **3 Animated Background Themes** — Cherry Blossom Garden, Night Cozy Room, and Pastel Clouds
- 🔊 **Sound Effects** *(toggleable)* — Synthesized pixel sounds for printing, task completion, and typing (Web Audio API — no external files)
- ✦ **Sparkle Bursts** — Completing a to-do triggers a burst of pixel sparkles
- 🧾 **Beautiful Receipt** — Torn paper edge, washi tape decoration, mood header, progress bar, affirmation box, and pixel category icons

***

## 🗂️ Project Structure

```
my-magical-day/
├── my-magical-day.html        ← Full standalone app (all CSS + JS inline)
│
├── index.html                 ← Original "Digital Typewriter" project (reference)
├── styles.css                 ← Original project styles
├── script.js                  ← Original project scripts
│
├── assets/
│   ├── printer.png            ← Pixel printer sprite
│   ├── heart.png              ← Pixel heart decoration
│   ├── button.png             ← Print button sprite
│   ├── event-personal-label.png
│   ├── event-work-label.png
│   ├── todo-personal-label.png
│   └── todo-work-label.png
│
└── README.md
```

> **Note:** `my-magical-day.html` is fully self-contained and works without any asset files — all decorations are CSS pixel-art. The original project (`index.html`) requires the `assets/` folder.

***

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Option 1 — Just open it (recommended)

No server, no build tools, no dependencies needed.

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/my-magical-day.git

# Open in your browser
open my-magical-day.html
# or just double-click the file in your file explorer
```

### Option 2 — Serve locally (for the original project with assets)

```bash
# Using Python
python -m http.server 8000

# Using Node.js
npx serve .
```

Then open `http://localhost:8000` in your browser.

***

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Technology | Usage |
|---|---|
| **Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS** | Everything — no frameworks |
| **Pixelify Sans** | Primary pixel font (Google Fonts) |
| **Press Start 2P** | Accent pixel font (Google Fonts) |
| **Web Audio API** | Synthesized sound effects (no audio files) |
| **CSS Animations** | All sparkles, printer motion, backgrounds |
| **CSS clip-path** | Torn receipt paper edge |
| **CSS box-shadow art** | Pixel decorations drawn in pure CSS |

No `npm install`. No build step. No backend. Pure web.

***

## 🎨 Design & Aesthetic

The visual style is **kawaii pixel art** — a blend of:

- 🎮 Stardew Valley cozy pixel art
- 🎀 Sanrio pastel softness
- 🎵 Lo-fi aesthetic calm

### Color Palette

| Name | Hex |
|---|---|
| Soft Pink | `#FFD9F2` |
| Lilac | `#F2D4FF` |
| Sky Blue | `#D5F1FF` |
| Mint | `#C8F5E8` |
