## 📋 How to Use

1. **Open** `my-magical-day.html` in any modern browser
2. **Add your events** — click ＋ to add events with time and category (personal / work / study / hobby)
3. **Add your to-dos** — click ＋ to add tasks with priority level (low / medium / high)
4. **Pick your mood** — choose from 6 pixel emoji moods at the top
5. **Switch background** — toggle between Cherry Blossom 🌸, Night Room 🌙, or Pastel Clouds ☁️
6. **Print your day** — click the **Print** button and watch the magic happen 🎉
7. **Check off tasks** on your receipt for sparkle bursts and progress bar updates
8. **New Day** — reset everything with the "New Day ✨" button

***

## 🌟 Highlights vs. Original Project

| Feature | Original (Digital Typewriter) | My Magical Day ✨ |
|---|---|---|
| Events & To-Dos | Hardcoded in HTML | Fully editable, add/delete live |
| Mood tracking | ❌ | ✅ 6 pixel moods |
| Progress bar | ❌ | ✅ Pixel health-bar style |
| Daily affirmations | ❌ | ✅ Rotating kawaii quotes |
| Background themes | Fixed gradient | ✅ 3 animated scenes |
| Sound effects | ❌ | ✅ Web Audio API synth sounds |
| Receipt design | Simple list | ✅ Washi tape, torn edge, mood, progress |
| Printer animation | Slides down | ✅ Bounces + heart confetti burst |
| Self-contained | No (needs assets folder) | ✅ Single HTML file |

